{"type": "article", "id": 12801, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-07-30T08:07:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 2357, "name": "花盆"}, {"id": 1130, "name": "手表"}, {"id": 1492, "name": "钱包"}, {"id": 11634, "name": "烤箱"}, {"id": 266, "name": "椅子"}, {"id": 13655, "name": "Manolo Blahnik"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000203NGImSAJDZaEPUe51.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tChair Collection by KARIMOKU\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>日本最近为了为 2020 年的奥运主办挪地方，决定拆除 1964 年的奥运主场馆，在原址上建一个新的竞技场。但他们没有把废旧的物品全部摧毁，而是回收了场馆内的蓝色坐垫，找来了三组新锐设计师，与日本木家具厂商 KARIMOKU 合作，一起推出了三款椅子，把蓝色坐垫重新利用，不仅珍藏多年前的记忆，同时也起到了宣传的作用。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123433YwOaDXLkGdy3tqom.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123434A561LK2tTGoJhaSr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123434iJw59kFTmzYpbGXv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123434koh4JdvEiagLjnYt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123435Lgi12Q8FtEnYlkda.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123435kfB3yJtWFwALMSoP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123436vgLX7epC49l2iAjO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071234365Ko1iyDRJaTQkMW9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123436ZHVhW8nSrMx6uP7N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071234374jFpclKCJdOioX6n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tMinimalist Coin Fold Wallet by Bellroy\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>尽管硬币时常被忽略，但不可否认的是我们的生活中仍然经常收到或是需要硬币，而硬币放在钱包里面，不仅弄得钱包看起来臃肿（虽然这样似乎也蛮酷），而且容易丢失。来自澳大利亚的品牌 Bellroy 最近推出了一个方便搁置硬币的钱包。他们在折叠钱包的一侧设计了一个搭扣，这样来组织硬币滑落。同时钱包可以安置 8 张卡，也设计了放置纸币的地方。钱包售价 99 美元，这是<a href=\"http://bellroy.com/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123437Z0L7fagbFOyIQxDM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123438VkfdhKvnl2PjbBxD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123438tiGcyTe0Ybr8BkH9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tPizza by Kristian Tapaninaho \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Kristian Tapaninaho 推出了一款微型烤箱，可以在两分钟内完成一个 Pizza 的烧烤，而且 Pizza 会带有柴烧的味道。设计师表示其设计初衷在于希望烤箱的 Pizza 也能够带有木头烧烤的香味，烤箱使用丝网不锈钢，可以 100％ 燃烧木屑，加速烧烤过程。除了烤 Pizza，这款烤箱也可以用于其他食物的烧烤。目前产品售价 299 美元，这是<a href=\"http://uuni.net/products/uuni-2\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123439zgLfB0MhiXu9Y7Vm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123439XAb498dLQspjV0u2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060712344083ayA5BCS6idGhgp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123440RGW30TwY5P8J2HzS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123441ETFaKN1SitjWCGfu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405027kuTP6nLNl2HVOrU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tModular Watch by Covair\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Covair 为了方便人家快速更换风格，推出了一款模块化的手表。这款表的表面和表带都是可以更换的，而磁铁链接的方式可以让人们迅速地更换，而不需要拆分各种零件。表带有皮革，不锈钢和尼龙三种材质可以选择，而表面也有白色和黑色，数字标示和抽象标示两种。目前产品正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/59168388/covair-interchangeable-watches-with-quick-change-s\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123441AaGvKi0TW5Xg9Bh4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123442bsy8BcA5kdlrPUKo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123442ljODIVHXifx0grMY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123443GEemJz1d5iXoLsZQ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66911765\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123444M9EGhX2RLm8VsdSe.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66911765\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123445zCXuxtniPTBL8rKF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49705882\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123445t2MnveXbgSA4KyRZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tConcrescence by Vako Design\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>来自爱荷华的设计工作室 Vako Design 最近推出了一个木制和水泥系列花盆，最大限度地为植物营造自然的生长氛围。花盆的底部支架由木材制成，组装简单，不含任何五金材料。而当支架组装好之后，水泥花盆可以放置在上面，如果希望降低花盆高度，则只需要把支架倒立放置即可。花盆有不同的规格可以选择，搭配不同的花草使用。这是<a href=\"http://www.vakodesign.com/#/tessellamp-1/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123446zpQiSDBAe75aHbqC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123446JgQPmkRf6bWlq7V8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123447rDJ9u85Ec7in1LUk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123447P8tE2oU5xdpcLOTv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123447jwLKYlyaRMVOW5v3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123448YyaM9mfjworKWZ0x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123448MtZSU6dvr5YJGqDc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123449f9Kwg1PhAsNtcO5S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tBag Collection by Manolo Blahnik \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>你有没有想过 Manolo Blahnik 变成包会是什么样子？这个酷酷的品牌 Manolo Blahnik 最近宣布要开始做包了，他们将会在这个月月底推出晚装包系列，会延续高跟鞋的风格，且共享设计风格。目前我们看到的预告里面，包包仍然走的华美路线。全线产品将会在明年春天发布，价格在 2000 美元左右。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123449cU8VHvXqt2MJOzPI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123449bgQfJ6UpdMD8ZPLE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123450pjg4sbLO8YnmB9kx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123450iIsnWDgkRMKcFzJT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}